Warning:
Half of this video is banter and I do swear a fair bit. I woke up early to do this so I don't really care. 
If you are sensitive to banter or swearing I would tell you not to watch the full version.
This is only banter and have no hate relation to any of the people I banter in this video such as:
Team Allah
Bad Company
Bezerk
Insidia
The Officals(I don't remember if I did your bit but just in case)
OCN

Just another heads up my mic is not the best and I know I did something to hurt your mic in the beginning of the video so please be careful if you are watching from the beginning.

Here is the version if you do not want to hear the banter. Please watch it from this link and pause it right after the song ends. 
https://youtu.be/U9d_X996NhA
If you want to hear the banter, I am not responsible if you take it the wrong way if I talk about you/your friends. You have been warned long enough to get mad at me and so I feel that 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U9d_X996NhA&feature=youtu.be
